bwapi

Class AIModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • bwapi.AIModule

  • public class AIModule
extends java.lang.Object
    This class receives all events from Broodwar. To process them, receive an AIModule's instance from Mirror and call setEventListener(bwapi.BWEventListener) to set you own listener. There's also a stub class (DefaultBWListener) provided, so you don't have to implement all of the methods.
